  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pericapsular nerve group block (PENG) has been deemed as a safe and effective regional&#xD;
      technique for postoperative pain after knee arthroscopy.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Pericapsular nerve group block(PENG) has been deemed as a safe and effective regional&#xD;
      technique for postoperative pain after knee artroscopy. Blockade of the branches of the&#xD;
      femoral and obturator nerves that provide innervation to any structures distal enough to be&#xD;
      useful in knee.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
